  id: wfo_wtetwc_02
  displayName: The President Wants to End the War
  description: "The country\u2019s president announces his intention to end the war.\nHe
    initiates official steps toward launching a peace process.\nThis move threatens
    existing power structures and ongoing plans.\nFor those benefiting from the continuation
    of the conflict, it poses a direct risk."
  devNote: 
  eventNote: "savunma bakan\u0131 sava\u015F\u0131 bitirmek istiyor eventinin daha
    zor halidir ve hareket alan\u0131m\u0131z k\u0131s\u0131tl\u0131d\u0131r"
